{"tid":485053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"既有印象 羊群心理 以及 法律程序","createTime":"2017-11-30T15:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T06:22:30.000Z","uid":52068,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e44dcb1251846a38b8b1159f9c1700a29faaadc5","tid":485053,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:17:21.000Z","msg":"首先睇一條我覺得幾有意思既片<br />\n特別希望你地深思<ins>4分40秒</ins>之後既內容<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hUDaKSRkHDo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhUDaKSRkHDo&d=3MzjoYWa7%2FEWPGoD32bGPSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=edde856d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hUDaKSRkHDo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事實</span><br />\no 男性犯罪機會比女性大<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">根據懲教處既資料，2016年6873名服刑人士中79%為男性</span><br />\no 而性罪犯當中，男性為極大多數。<br />\no 亞洲地區性定罪率高<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">日本中國近100%<br />\n台灣86.6%</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既有印象</span><br />\n依個事實令到我地每一個人都存在住一個<ins>既有印象</ins>：<br />\n性侵事件<ins>真實存在</ins><br />\n在性罪案中男性係<ins>施害者</ins>，女性係<ins>受害者</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">羊群心理</span><br />\n當一個性侵指控出現個時，<ins>基於既有印象</ins>好多人都會認為性侵事件真實存在，形成主流思想。<br />\n經過越黎越多人<ins>受羊群心理影響</ins>，我地偏向<ins>拋棄理性同邏輯</ins>，去<ins>迎合主流思想</ins>，在證實真相<ins>之前</ins>，認為性侵事件真實存在，令到依一件未經證實既事<ins>看似越黎越可信</ins>。<br />\n<br />\n從而咬定<ins>疑犯</ins>肯定有做過，係一個<ins>罪犯</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">法律程序</span><br />\n不過，根據無罪推定原則，疑犯在未在審訊中判處<ins>罪成前</ins>，<ins>必須假設疑犯或者被告均為<strong>清白無罪</strong></ins>。這原則<ins>貫穿</ins>香港刑事訴訟程序的<ins>每一步驟</ins>。而我認為我地係對待類似事件都要用咁既方式思考<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n係真相大白、係法庭有定案之前，保持<ins>理性</ins><ins>批判</ins>討論"},{"pid":"60242c42c990e8aa3c4a2138df68536ce2470f12","tid":485053,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>經crosscheck多個post，最新確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: red;\">三色貓</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">法國佬巫斯義</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">極右派政治家</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Coffee@</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Gladiclus</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">newlife</span></del>、JR、RedBaron = Epiphany、dewi、bbchu、D_Wade、Spurs_Leonard、十卜Ching、侵B、民國復興、群龍共舞、霍金轉身、優美開始、黑腸盧卡庫 = 國語好手、返六日唔撚易、追捕兩米黑鬼、吾系甘開心牙、社會主義者佛利民、小翁翁、毛澤東、晚媚</strong></span>"},{"pid":"68432414d992c9108a521dfeaf8a41bdd37c450b","tid":485053,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70b3eb35c588dad6a7a36e2e95433144c52ddc0","tid":485053,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab663e5e183eff064ffa7dbcaacbd767d3851510","tid":485053,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2812ea6a80bfa03f20aa271d9ee469f5e54da110","tid":485053,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342e7c9ff72770d76a0f1276a1d7bfa29c072c6b","tid":485053,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77691a7647a0cd0be8c9ce827e521bfeace0a7b6","tid":485053,"uid":57705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:22:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62bacd477b0ff39b6cf63afce9de4c27ae3941f3","tid":485053,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:23:45.000Z","msg":"某女權撚就喺度係咁強調啲既有印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d249bcbb45a35aaeaff9e414a2361618971cd645","tid":485053,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:35:20.000Z","msg":"呢個post好高質<br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59050e137f021d33819cd3e45faa3706bae0b07e","tid":485053,"uid":45788,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:48:56.000Z","msg":"比較留意最尾個part<br />\n<br />\n香港依家好多人正正片中所講<br />\n<br />\n比情感控制，以個人情感批判他人<br />\n成日比主流傳媒報道/傳聞拉住行<br />\n只係一味覺得受害者好慘，所以佢講嘅野係真<br />\n而背後唔經專業判斷/調查就包大人上身<br />\n<br />\n更諷刺嘅係，好多人以香港法制為榮，覺得佢能夠發揮法治精神保護市民<br />\n但香港法治講究無罪推定，而佢地就正正做大法官上身未審先判破壞無罪推定精神<br />\n呢個係自打嘴巴定精神分裂？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢單野我唔敢講係個運動員屈人定真有其事<br />\n但請唔好做道德判官<br />\n你想做，可以返中国，個度行有罪推定論<br />\n<br />\n如果香港人真係咁想保護香港法治<br />\n唔該留番香港司法機構做野<br />\n<br />\n你地做緊道德判官個陣，正正就係破壞長久以來香港法治精神，同埋咁耐以黎嘅邏輯知識"},{"pid":"2c2bf5f591dbe2cbf2d380b1c98ad2a320c442e7","tid":485053,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:51:53.000Z","msg":"呢個post要畀啲力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f72771a9524330cde0793d086d8d003158ed151","tid":485053,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:52:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"28350186c61d008acb981d9fa999a0344a970b56","tid":485053,"uid":22040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:54:02.000Z","msg":"少有高質post"},{"pid":"a57dd2121241bcfac01790090b17ed6434cfc152","tid":485053,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"peer pressure"},{"pid":"f7167d014d6385a341e310d307651eeb899924ec","tid":485053,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dc634fb710dfb6ad6503b9c0172a93ee6fd172","tid":485053,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64bf1150b715ede12c6084922868c70b03a82f1","tid":485053,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4070adb9c60bc45fe8c9e77de4545877e2f0a4f6","tid":485053,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實傳媒咁報法，仲要追住個前教練<br />\n某程度上佢就算被告，已經好難獲得公平審訊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n相信律政司唔會告<br />\n告都冇可能入到罪"},{"pid":"24eecfc78e4c4c5a7fe42639fd8911d614744d46","tid":485053,"uid"